{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock","slug":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock","title":"The Secret of the Tide Clock","title_ko":"조수 시계의 비밀","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/cover.webp","summary_ko":"미나가 바닷가 할아버지의 낡은 조수 시계가 어떻게 바다를 읽는지 알아내고, 다가오는 폭풍에서 배들을 지켜내요.","wordCount":309,"pages":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mina lived in a small village beside the gray sea.","translation_ko":"미나는 잿빛 바다 옆 작은 마을에 살았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"lived","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":440,"endMs":800},{"word":"in","charStart":11,"charEnd":13,"startMs":800,"endMs":940},{"word":"a","charStart":14,"charEnd":15,"startMs":940,"endMs":1200},{"word":"small","charStart":16,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1540},{"word":"village","charStart":22,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1880},{"word":"beside","charStart":30,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2320},{"word":"the","charStart":37,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2620},{"word":"gray","charStart":41,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2860},{"word":"sea","charStart":46,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2860,"endMs":3120}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Her grandfather was a fisher, and his boat smelled of salt and rope.","translation_ko":"할아버지는 어부였고, 배에서는 소금과 밧줄 냄새가 났어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Her","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"grandfather","charStart":4,"charEnd":15,"startMs":260,"endMs":760},{"word":"was","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":760,"endMs":1060},{"word":"a","charStart":20,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1520},{"word":"fisher","charStart":22,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1520},{"word":"and","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2180},{"word":"his","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2440},{"word":"boat","charStart":38,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2700},{"word":"smelled","charStart":43,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2700,"endMs":3040},{"word":"of","charStart":51,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3600},{"word":"salt","charStart":54,"charEnd":58,"startMs":3600,"endMs":3600},{"word":"and","charStart":59,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3600,"endMs":4160},{"word":"rope","charStart":63,"charEnd":67,"startMs":4160,"endMs":4360}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"On the wall hung an old wooden clock with a single hand.","translation_ko":"벽에는 바늘이 하나뿐인 낡은 나무 시계가 걸려 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"On","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"the","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":380,"endMs":820},{"word":"wall","charStart":7,"charEnd":11,"startMs":820,"endMs":1120},{"word":"hung","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1600},{"word":"an","charStart":17,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1980},{"word":"old","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2380},{"word":"wooden","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2620},{"word":"clock","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2620,"endMs":3040},{"word":"with","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3520},{"word":"a","charStart":42,"charEnd":43,"startMs":3520,"endMs":3880},{"word":"single","charStart":44,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3880,"endMs":4040},{"word":"hand","charStart":51,"charEnd":55,"startMs":4040,"endMs":4400}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"Grandfather called it the tide clock, and he watched it every morning.","translation_ko":"할아버지는 그것을 조수 시계라고 부르며 아침마다 들여다보았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Grandfather","charStart":0,"charEnd":11,"startMs":0,"endMs":620},{"word":"called","charStart":12,"charEnd":18,"startMs":620,"endMs":960},{"word":"it","charStart":19,"charEnd":21,"startMs":960,"endMs":1140},{"word":"the","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1300},{"word":"tide","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1600},{"word":"clock","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1940},{"word":"and","charStart":38,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2440},{"word":"he","charStart":42,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2640},{"word":"watched","charStart":45,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2880},{"word":"it","charStart":53,"charEnd":55,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3140},{"word":"every","charStart":56,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3140,"endMs":3540},{"word":"morning","charStart":62,"charEnd":69,"startMs":3540,"endMs":3800}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"How does it know the sea?\" Mina asked one quiet day.","translation_ko":"\"이게 어떻게 바다를 알아요?\" 어느 조용한 날 미나가 물었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"How","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"does","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":260,"endMs":520},{"word":"it","charStart":10,"charEnd":12,"startMs":520,"endMs":700},{"word":"know","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":700,"endMs":880},{"word":"the","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":880,"endMs":1180},{"word":"sea","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1480},{"word":"Mina","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2160},{"word":"asked","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2600},{"word":"one","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2920},{"word":"quiet","charStart":43,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2920,"endMs":3280},{"word":"day","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3280,"endMs":3600}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"Grandfather only smiled and tapped the wood with his thumb.","translation_ko":"할아버지는 그저 미소를 지으며 엄지로 나무를 톡톡 두드렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Grandfather","charStart":0,"charEnd":11,"startMs":0,"endMs":560},{"word":"only","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":560,"endMs":1060},{"word":"smiled","charStart":17,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1400},{"word":"and","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1760},{"word":"tapped","charStart":28,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1760,"endMs":1960},{"word":"the","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2240},{"word":"wood","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2320},{"word":"with","charStart":44,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2560},{"word":"his","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2760},{"word":"thumb","charStart":53,"charEnd":58,"startMs":2760,"endMs":2960}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"Each day she watched the hand move, slow and steady.","translation_ko":"날마다 미나는 바늘이 느리고 일정하게 움직이는 모습을 지켜보았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Each","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"day","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":300,"endMs":780},{"word":"she","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":940,"endMs":1320},{"word":"watched","charStart":13,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1700},{"word":"the","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1980},{"word":"hand","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2320},{"word":"move","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2760},{"word":"slow","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3500},{"word":"and","charStart":41,"charEnd":44,"startMs":3500,"endMs":4100},{"word":"steady","charStart":45,"charEnd":51,"startMs":4100,"endMs":4320}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"When it pointed up, the water rose; when it pointed down, the water pulled away.","translation_ko":"바늘이 위를 가리키면 물이 차올랐고, 아래를 가리키면 물이 빠져나갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"it","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":220,"endMs":400},{"word":"pointed","charStart":8,"charEnd":15,"startMs":400,"endMs":600},{"word":"up","charStart":16,"charEnd":18,"startMs":600,"endMs":920},{"word":"the","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1240},{"word":"water","charStart":24,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1420},{"word":"rose","charStart":30,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1780},{"word":"when","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2280},{"word":"it","charStart":41,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2660},{"word":"pointed","charStart":44,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2660},{"word":"down","charStart":52,"charEnd":56,"startMs":2660,"endMs":3100},{"word":"the","charStart":58,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3380,"endMs":3540},{"word":"water","charStart":62,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3540,"endMs":3700},{"word":"pulled","charStart":68,"charEnd":74,"startMs":3700,"endMs":3920},{"word":"away","charStart":75,"charEnd":79,"startMs":3920,"endMs":4200}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"Then Mina noticed something strange about the moon.","translation_ko":"그러다 미나는 달에 관한 이상한 점을 알아챘어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"Mina","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":300,"endMs":620},{"word":"noticed","charStart":10,"charEnd":17,"startMs":620,"endMs":1060},{"word":"something","charStart":18,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1420},{"word":"strange","charStart":28,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1420,"endMs":2040},{"word":"about","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2300},{"word":"the","charStart":42,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2500},{"word":"moon","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2660}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"When the moon was full and round, the high tide climbed even higher.","translation_ko":"달이 둥글고 가득 차면, 밀물은 평소보다 더 높이 올라왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":280,"endMs":600},{"word":"moon","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":600,"endMs":760},{"word":"was","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":760,"endMs":1120},{"word":"full","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1420},{"word":"and","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1760},{"word":"round","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2180},{"word":"the","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2780,"endMs":2880},{"word":"high","charStart":38,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3160},{"word":"tide","charStart":43,"charEnd":47,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3440},{"word":"climbed","charStart":48,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3840},{"word":"even","charStart":56,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3840,"endMs":4260},{"word":"higher","charStart":61,"charEnd":67,"startMs":4260,"endMs":4580}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"The clock follows the moon!\" she whispered, her eyes wide.","translation_ko":"\"시계가 달을 따라가는 거였어!\" 미나가 눈을 크게 뜨며 속삭였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"clock","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":240,"endMs":780},{"word":"follows","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":780,"endMs":1580},{"word":"the","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1900},{"word":"moon","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2120},{"word":"she","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2840},{"word":"whispered","charStart":34,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2840,"endMs":3280},{"word":"her","charStart":45,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3460,"endMs":3780},{"word":"eyes","charStart":49,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3780,"endMs":4000},{"word":"wide","charStart":54,"charEnd":58,"startMs":4000,"endMs":4420}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"Grandfather nodded, because at last she had found the secret herself.","translation_ko":"할아버지가 고개를 끄덕였어요. 미나가 마침내 스스로 비밀을 찾아냈으니까요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Grandfather","charStart":0,"charEnd":11,"startMs":820,"endMs":1420},{"word":"nodded","charStart":12,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1820},{"word":"because","charStart":20,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2360},{"word":"at","charStart":28,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2580},{"word":"last","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2920},{"word":"she","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":3260,"endMs":3260},{"word":"had","charStart":40,"charEnd":43,"startMs":3260,"endMs":3440},{"word":"found","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3660},{"word":"the","charStart":50,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3660,"endMs":3920},{"word":"secret","charStart":54,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3920,"endMs":4140},{"word":"herself","charStart":61,"charEnd":68,"startMs":4140,"endMs":4660}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"The moon pulls the water like a quiet hand,\" he said.","translation_ko":"\"달이 조용한 손처럼 물을 끌어당긴단다.\" 할아버지가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"moon","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":240,"endMs":560},{"word":"pulls","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":560,"endMs":880},{"word":"the","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":880,"endMs":1120},{"word":"water","charStart":20,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1340},{"word":"like","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1580},{"word":"a","charStart":31,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1920},{"word":"quiet","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2120},{"word":"hand","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2520},{"word":"he","charStart":46,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3040},{"word":"said","charStart":49,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3320}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"And this old clock simply listens.\"","translation_ko":"\"그리고 이 낡은 시계는 그저 그 소리에 귀를 기울일 뿐이지.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"And","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"this","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":340,"endMs":820},{"word":"old","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":820,"endMs":1180},{"word":"clock","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1520},{"word":"simply","charStart":20,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1520,"endMs":2260},{"word":"listens","charStart":27,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2660}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"One afternoon the sky turned a heavy, bruised gray.","translation_ko":"어느 오후, 하늘이 짙고 멍든 듯한 잿빛으로 변했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"afternoon","charStart":4,"charEnd":13,"startMs":400,"endMs":940},{"word":"the","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1500},{"word":"sky","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1680},{"word":"turned","charStart":22,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1680,"endMs":2080},{"word":"a","charStart":29,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2440},{"word":"heavy","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2840},{"word":"bruised","charStart":38,"charEnd":45,"startMs":3220,"endMs":3360},{"word":"gray","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3780}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"The wind grew sharp, and far away the fishing boats were still out at sea.","translation_ko":"바람이 날카로워졌고, 저 멀리 고깃배들은 아직 바다에 나가 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"wind","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":240,"endMs":560},{"word":"grew","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":560,"endMs":900},{"word":"sharp","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":900,"endMs":1280},{"word":"and","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1680},{"word":"far","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1920},{"word":"away","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2180},{"word":"the","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2360},{"word":"fishing","charStart":38,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2660},{"word":"boats","charStart":46,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2960},{"word":"were","charStart":52,"charEnd":56,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3200},{"word":"still","charStart":57,"charEnd":62,"startMs":3200,"endMs":3520},{"word":"out","charStart":63,"charEnd":66,"startMs":3520,"endMs":3700},{"word":"at","charStart":67,"charEnd":69,"startMs":3700,"endMs":3920},{"word":"sea","charStart":70,"charEnd":73,"startMs":3920,"endMs":4060}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mina ran to the clock and saw the hand point to an unusually high tide.","translation_ko":"미나는 시계로 달려갔고, 바늘이 유난히 높은 조수를 가리키는 것을 보았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"ran","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":400,"endMs":740},{"word":"to","charStart":9,"charEnd":11,"startMs":740,"endMs":900},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":900,"endMs":1300},{"word":"clock","charStart":16,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1320},{"word":"and","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1740},{"word":"saw","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1740,"endMs":1840},{"word":"the","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2060},{"word":"hand","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2380},{"word":"point","charStart":39,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2660},{"word":"to","charStart":45,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2860},{"word":"an","charStart":48,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2860,"endMs":3060},{"word":"unusually","charStart":51,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3060,"endMs":3600},{"word":"high","charStart":61,"charEnd":65,"startMs":3600,"endMs":4000},{"word":"tide","charStart":66,"charEnd":70,"startMs":4000,"endMs":4280}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p9-s2","ord":1,"text":"The tide was rising too fast, far too fast, and a storm was racing toward the shore.","translation_ko":"조수가 너무 빠르게, 너무도 빠르게 차오르고 있었고, 폭풍이 해안으로 달려오고 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p9-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"tide","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":360,"endMs":380},{"word":"was","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":380,"endMs":620},{"word":"rising","charStart":13,"charEnd":19,"startMs":620,"endMs":960},{"word":"too","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":960,"endMs":1340},{"word":"fast","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1720},{"word":"far","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2300},{"word":"too","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2540},{"word":"fast","charStart":38,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2540,"endMs":2900},{"word":"and","charStart":44,"charEnd":47,"startMs":3300,"endMs":3320},{"word":"a","charStart":48,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3320,"endMs":3620},{"word":"storm","charStart":50,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3800},{"word":"was","charStart":56,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3800,"endMs":4100},{"word":"racing","charStart":60,"charEnd":66,"startMs":4100,"endMs":4360},{"word":"toward","charStart":67,"charEnd":73,"startMs":4360,"endMs":4600},{"word":"the","charStart":74,"charEnd":77,"startMs":4600,"endMs":4920},{"word":"shore","charStart":78,"charEnd":83,"startMs":4920,"endMs":4960}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p10","pageNo":10,"spread":"p10","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p10.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p10-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"Grandfather, the clock is warning us!\" she cried.","translation_ko":"\"할아버지, 시계가 우리에게 경고하고 있어요!\" 미나가 소리쳤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p10-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Grandfather","charStart":1,"charEnd":12,"startMs":0,"endMs":520},{"word":"the","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":880,"endMs":980},{"word":"clock","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":980,"endMs":1160},{"word":"is","charStart":24,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1380},{"word":"warning","charStart":27,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1560},{"word":"us","charStart":35,"charEnd":37,"startMs":1560,"endMs":2340},{"word":"she","charStart":40,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2460},{"word":"cried","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2740}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p10-s2","ord":1,"text":"He understood at once and rang the great bell on the harbor wall.","translation_ko":"할아버지는 곧바로 알아채고 항구 벽에 걸린 커다란 종을 울렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p10-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"understood","charStart":3,"charEnd":13,"startMs":260,"endMs":740},{"word":"at","charStart":14,"charEnd":16,"startMs":740,"endMs":1140},{"word":"once","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1400},{"word":"and","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1840},{"word":"rang","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1840,"endMs":1880},{"word":"the","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2100},{"word":"great","charStart":35,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2400},{"word":"bell","charStart":41,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2660},{"word":"on","charStart":46,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2860},{"word":"the","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2860,"endMs":3140},{"word":"harbor","charStart":53,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3140,"endMs":3240},{"word":"wall","charStart":60,"charEnd":64,"startMs":3240,"endMs":3560}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p11","pageNo":11,"spread":"p11","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p11.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p11-s1","ord":0,"text":"The deep sound rolled across the water like a voice.","translation_ko":"묵직한 소리가 마치 목소리처럼 물 위로 퍼져 나갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p11-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"deep","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":260,"endMs":580},{"word":"sound","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":580,"endMs":980},{"word":"rolled","charStart":15,"charEnd":21,"startMs":980,"endMs":1280},{"word":"across","charStart":22,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1620},{"word":"the","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1880},{"word":"water","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2080},{"word":"like","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2460},{"word":"a","charStart":44,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2680},{"word":"voice","charStart":46,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2680,"endMs":2900}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p11-s2","ord":1,"text":"One by one the boats turned and hurried home before the worst could reach them.","translation_ko":"배들은 하나둘 뱃머리를 돌려, 가장 거센 폭풍이 닥치기 전에 서둘러 돌아왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p11-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"by","charStart":4,"charEnd":6,"startMs":380,"endMs":620},{"word":"one","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":620,"endMs":900},{"word":"the","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1660},{"word":"boats","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1660},{"word":"turned","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2040},{"word":"and","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2360},{"word":"hurried","charStart":32,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2540},{"word":"home","charStart":40,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2540,"endMs":2900},{"word":"before","charStart":45,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3160},{"word":"the","charStart":52,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3420},{"word":"worst","charStart":56,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3420,"endMs":3680},{"word":"could","charStart":62,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3680,"endMs":3940},{"word":"reach","charStart":68,"charEnd":73,"startMs":3940,"endMs":4180},{"word":"them","charStart":74,"charEnd":78,"startMs":4180,"endMs":4400}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p12","pageNo":12,"spread":"p12","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p12.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p12-s1","ord":0,"text":"Rain fell hard, but every fisher stood safe on the shore.","translation_ko":"비가 세차게 쏟아졌지만, 모든 어부가 무사히 해안에 서 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p12-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Rain","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"fell","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":400,"endMs":700},{"word":"hard","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":700,"endMs":1100},{"word":"but","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1580},{"word":"every","charStart":20,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1900},{"word":"fisher","charStart":26,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2220},{"word":"stood","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2580},{"word":"safe","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2920},{"word":"on","charStart":44,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2920,"endMs":3060},{"word":"the","charStart":47,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3060,"endMs":3260},{"word":"shore","charStart":51,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3260,"endMs":3420}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p12-s2","ord":1,"text":"They thanked Mina, and her cheeks grew warm with quiet pride.","translation_ko":"사람들은 미나에게 고마워했고, 미나는 조용히 뿌듯해서 두 볼이 따뜻해졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p12-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"thanked","charStart":5,"charEnd":12,"startMs":280,"endMs":560},{"word":"Mina","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":560,"endMs":820},{"word":"and","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1320},{"word":"her","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1480},{"word":"cheeks","charStart":27,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1740},{"word":"grew","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1740,"endMs":1980},{"word":"warm","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2380},{"word":"with","charStart":44,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2640},{"word":"quiet","charStart":49,"charEnd":54,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2980},{"word":"pride","charStart":55,"charEnd":60,"startMs":2980,"endMs":3360}]}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p13","pageNo":13,"spread":"p13","imageUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/p13.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p13-s1","ord":0,"text":"That night the storm passed, and the moon shone clear again.","translation_ko":"그날 밤 폭풍이 지나가고, 달이 다시 맑게 빛났어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p13-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"That","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"night","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":320,"endMs":660},{"word":"the","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":660,"endMs":1020},{"word":"storm","charStart":15,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1300},{"word":"passed","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1800},{"word":"and","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2420},{"word":"the","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2680},{"word":"moon","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2680,"endMs":2920},{"word":"shone","charStart":42,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2920,"endMs":3280},{"word":"clear","charStart":48,"charEnd":53,"startMs":3280,"endMs":3660},{"word":"again","charStart":54,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3660,"endMs":4020}]},{"id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-p13-s2","ord":1,"text":"Mina looked at the old clock and understood that the sea was not magic, only a patient secret waiting to be read.","translation_ko":"미나는 낡은 시계를 바라보며, 바다는 마법이 아니라 차분히 살피면 읽을 수 있는 비밀이라는 것을 깨달았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-secret-of-the-tide-clock/audio/p13-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"looked","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":460,"endMs":960},{"word":"at","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":960,"endMs":1120},{"word":"the","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1240},{"word":"old","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1740},{"word":"clock","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2060},{"word":"and","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2680},{"word":"understood","charStart":33,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2680,"endMs":3080},{"word":"that","charStart":44,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3340},{"word":"the","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3340,"endMs":3620},{"word":"sea","charStart":53,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3760},{"word":"was","charStart":57,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3760,"endMs":4020},{"word":"not","charStart":61,"charEnd":64,"startMs":4020,"endMs":4380},{"word":"magic","charStart":65,"charEnd":70,"startMs":4380,"endMs":4800},{"word":"only","charStart":72,"charEnd":76,"startMs":5520,"endMs":5660},{"word":"a","charStart":77,"charEnd":78,"startMs":5660,"endMs":5880},{"word":"patient","charStart":79,"charEnd":86,"startMs":5880,"endMs":6280},{"word":"secret","charStart":87,"charEnd":93,"startMs":6280,"endMs":6700},{"word":"waiting","charStart":94,"charEnd":101,"startMs":6700,"endMs":7120},{"word":"to","charStart":102,"charEnd":104,"startMs":7120,"endMs":7340},{"word":"be","charStart":105,"charEnd":107,"startMs":7340,"endMs":7540},{"word":"read","charStart":108,"charEnd":112,"startMs":7540,"endMs":7700}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"할아버지가 벽에 걸어 둔 시계를 무엇이라고 불렀나요?","type":"mc","options":["바람 시계","조수 시계","별 시계","모래 시계"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"할아버지는 바늘이 하나뿐인 그 낡은 나무 시계를 조수 시계라고 불렀어요.","id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"미나는 밀물이 더 높이 차오를 때 하늘에서 무엇을 보았나요?","type":"mc","options":["두꺼운 구름","떨어지는 별","둥글게 가득 찬 달","붉은 해"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"달이 둥글고 가득 찼을 때 밀물이 더 높이 올라온다는 것을 미나가 알아챘어요.","id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"할아버지의 말에 따르면 물을 끌어당기는 것은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["달","항구의 종","시계의 바늘","바람"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"할아버지는 달이 조용한 손처럼 물을 끌어당긴다고 설명했어요.","id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"폭풍이 다가올 때 배들을 불러들이기 위해 할아버지가 한 일은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["항구의 큰 종을 울렸다","등불을 껐다","바다로 노를 저어 나갔다","시계를 멈췄다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"할아버지는 항구 벽의 커다란 종을 울려 배들이 서둘러 돌아오게 했어요.","id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 전하려는 마음은 무엇에 가장 가까운가요?","type":"mc","options":["자연은 마법이 아니라 호기심으로 읽어낼 수 있는 비밀이다","오래된 물건은 쓸모가 없다","바다는 언제나 두려워해야 한다","혼자 있는 것이 가장 안전하다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"미나는 바다가 마법이 아니라 차분히 살피면 읽어낼 수 있는 비밀임을 깨달았어요.","id":"the-secret-of-the-tide-clock-q5","ord":4}]}